List of desired improvements for this module.

In the first column a (*) is this feature is still missing
or a version number indicating the version in which it has been introduced.

(0.0.1)	Use Tar module instead of relying on system tar executable, particularly needed for Windows integration

(*)	Add validation schema to configuration file

(*) Allow multi-plan (different <plan> tags) in the configuration and pass plan name to input

(*) Add more time frequencies (e.g.) hours, weeks to favour real-time instead of overnight behaviour

(*) Manage synching with external drive, detecting when it becomes connected

(*) Graphical front-end to manage configuration and interactive behaviour